Healing sound artist, poet, singer and soul searcher. I create songs and poetry that help your heart open and release suppressed feelings in a gentle way. My poems and songs help you tune in to the states of freedom, love, harmony and self-realization. They help you live your life to the full of your potential. ...read more

Maria quit her career to help people cope with burn-out, stress, depression and anxiety. Her approach is in building strong connections with the body and emotions. Preventive measures are wiser, and Maria helps develop an outlook of non-judgement, compassion and self-support. Maria is a mindfulness teacher, a CFT therapist, a level two Reiki master, and graduated from the TT2 level of MBSR. Maria has practiced Tibetan buddhist meditation since 2016 as a disciple of Mingyur Rinpoche....read more
I work as a psychologist in Moscow and online.
Professional psychologist, Coach, Author of meditations

I was born in 1972 on Sakhalin Island and have been involved in Eastern practices since childhood; experienced in martial arts, intellectual practices, social disciplines and science. On a wave of enthusiasm for consciousness, I extract constructive elements from meditative methods for practical solutions of typical human problems. I do not lead schools; occasionally give private lessons individually and in groups....read more

Dayanand Das Maharaj is a spiritual teacher, healing practitioner, coach, with 20 years of experience guiding individuals and groups in their journey of personal transformation and conscious evolution. He holds the title of Mahamandaleshwara in the Vishnu Swami lineage and His unique approach brings together the ancient wisdom of the East, Hebrew mysticism, and esoteric energy work to make the transformative power of spiritual wisdom accessible and practical for daily life.
